# hdparm

##### Force spin-down of external hard-drive

   hdparm  -y /dev/sda

##### Set the standby time of a hard drive

   hdparm  -S5 /dev/sda

##### Testing hard disk reading speed

   hdparm  -t /dev/sda

##### Detail info about the hard disk

   hdparm  verbose /dev/sda1

##### Testing hard disk reading speed

   hdparm  -t /dev/sda
